Afro fusion artiste, Burna Boy has made another history as he has been adjudged the overall Best Artiste in Africa. He also won Best Male Artiste  from West Africa award. The hit maker, who few days ago was nominated for a Grammy  award in the Best World Music Album category defeated the likes of Davido and Wizkid to clinch the  award. He was at the event to pick his award. Also, Wizkid won the song of the year award. Vanguard By Benjamin Njoku Afro fusion artiste, Burna Boy has made another history as he has been adjudged the overall Best Artiste in Africa. He also won Best Male Artiste from West Africa award. The hit maker, who few days ago was nominated for a Grammy award in the Best World… November 24, 2019 In "Entertainment" Afro-fusion star, Damini Ogulu aka Burna Boy, has clinched the most wins at the 2019 Soundcity MVP Awards, taking home four plaques including ‘African Artiste of the Year’. January 6, 2019 In "Music" Afropop star David ‘Davido’ Adeleke, Afro-fusion singer, Burna Boy and South African musician Nasty C scored the most nominations for 2019 AFRIMA awards. August 26, 2019 In "Entertainment"